- Bronze: `docs/bronze-architecture.md` y `docs/ingestion-strategy.md`.
- Silver: `docs/silver-architecture.md`, `docs/silver-data-quality.md` y `docs/silver-execution-guide.md`.
- Auditoría: `docs/audit-model.md`.
